# Code owners — GitHub auto-requests review from these accounts on every PR.
# Combined with "Require review from Code Owners" in branch protection, this
# enforces that an admin / team lead must approve before a PR can be merged.
#
# TODO: replace the placeholders with real GitHub usernames or @org/team slugs.
#       Lines are last-match-wins; the catch-all below covers the whole repo.

# Whole repository (admins / team leads):
*               @ADMIN_USERNAME @TEAMLEAD_USERNAME

